Xcoral is a multiwindow mouse-based text editor for Unix and X Window
System. Syntax highlighting and auto-indentation are available. A
built-in browser enables you to navigate through C functions, C++ and
Java classes, methods and files. A SMall Ansi C Interpreter (Smac) is
also built-in to dynamically extend the editor's possibilities (user
functions, key bindings, modes etc). Xcoral provides regions and marks,
kill-buffers, macros system and unlimited undo.
